parameters: \nc<NPC 2 under Hypnosis>S-Sorry. My body is moving on its own...!

\TA[1]Say whatever you want. In the end, what matters is the
result.

\TA[1]No matter what you say, it's just the howling of a loser if
you can't produce the result of defeating me.

\TA[1]In the end, all that matters is for people to be happy. I
will make that happen!

\TA[1]Well, they're just children after all. They're not worth
talking to.
\TA[1]Now, everyone, go ahead and do it!
\nc<Citizen 2>The child who drove away Black Muscle, right?
\TA[1]Certainly, they are stronger than those little kids.

\TA[1]No matter how strong they may be, magical girls cannot harm
the citizens.

\TA[1](Kuh, I can't attack properly when surrounded by
citizens....) (And there are an incredible number of them.)

\TA[1]Did these people jump down from the second floor?!
(Villains?... No, they're just people...)

\TA[1]Hohoho. As expected, I can't overwhelm you with numbers.
However, you also have your limits in terms of stamina.

\TA[1](Individually, their power isn't much, but when they
gather, it becomes troublesome.) (Over there, they are
protected by the citizens.)

\TA[1](Ah, geez! If only I had been a little faster, I could have
taken advantage of the opening all at once...!)

\TA[1]Hmm? A mascot, huh? Since you can't do anything, are you
saying you'll at least cheer us on?
\nc<Citizen 3>Well, don't lose, Levantia! Knock them out!

\TA[1](The emotions of the citizens are turning into power... Now
is the time!)
\TA[1]Phew... Today is my loss, isn't it?

\TA[1]Levantia, you say? With her perfect appearance and the
darkness hidden within her heart...

\TA[1]You're saying things like a fake fortune teller. Stop
saying weird things and come down!

\TA[1]Oops, I can't do that. If I lose my power, everyone's
happiness will be lost too.

\nc<>Let's prepare a little more carefully and meet again next
time.
\nc<Citizen 1 whose hypnosis has been lifted>I... I won... I won!!
\nc<Citizen 2 whose hypnosis has been lifted>Wow, Levantia! Thanks to you, I was saved!
\TA[1](No... I can't help it, my mouth just loosens up.)

\TA[1](It's been a while since I've received this much
attention.) (Somehow, it feels a little different from
before...)
\nc<Citizens>All three of you, do your best~!
